網 址
http://www.crisp-dm.org/


內容簡介
The CRISP-DM project has developed an industry- and tool-neutral 
            Data Mining process model. Starting from the embryonic knowledge discovery 
            processes used in industry today and responding directly to user requirements, 
            this project defined and validated a data mining process that is applicable 
            in diverse industry sectors. This will make large data mining projects 
            faster, cheaper, more reliable and more manageable.


 

